{"tid":2325120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派總辭　立會極速「人大化」　舉手過撥款　政策零提問　誇林鄭「超人」","createTime":"2020-12-14T11:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T12:23:00.000Z","uid":271829,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a182e1e399657a6801545e268f3438d8ead97803","tid":2325120,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YJlIxH6OwknaJFV7jOxWtnbfreo=/4859x2733/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RO3YYEVFGFHRJBGT4TTFMIP4GU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYJlIxH6OwknaJFV7jOxWtnbfreo%3D%2F4859x2733%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRO3YYEVFGFHRJBGT4TTFMIP4GU.JPG&h=71329fed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在《施政報告》答問大會，建制派在會議廳淪為林鄭月娥的「誇誇群」。<br />\n....<br />\n缺少民主派監察下，立法會不少會議亦淪為「人大式」舉手會議，立法會工務小組就試過僅用了一小時，即舉手通過政府涉款高達70億元的4項工程建議，開會時間比平日長逾兩小時明顯縮短。其中涉款近3億元公帑的撥款建議，更在無任何議員提問下舉手通過，令一眾當日原在會議廳預備解答議員提問的官員，與會不足兩分鐘後就輕鬆離開。<br />\n<br />\n過去總會激發示威場面的《施政報告》答問大會，在民主派議員離開後亦一片「河蟹」，只餘建制派在會議廳為特首林鄭月娥充當「誇誇群」，其中以經民聯林健鋒最令人嘆為觀止，一度大讚林鄭「仲叻過超人，有計有謀，又打得」。<br />\n<br />\n除了議會的反對聲音消失，平日經常出現議員排隊發言的立法會採訪區亦明顯較過去死寂，即使有線大裁員事件全港譁然，包括聲稱關注勞工權益的工聯會在內的建制派，當日未見任何議員在立法會就該事發表意見。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201214/AVAGGZH2PBBCFE7HUW7USBXURY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201214%2FAVAGGZH2PBBCFE7HUW7USBXURY%2F&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7nwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=80c1e603\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201214%2FAVAGGZH2PBBCFE7HUW7USBXURY%2F&h=d314102a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201214/AVAGGZH2PBBCFE7HUW7USBXURY/</a>"},{"pid":"ac8530837ff648ee2a8021884e7ba400e1d7365f","tid":2325120,"uid":115579,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:03:04.000Z","msg":"呢個其實就係爭議，不過只係時間問題"},{"pid":"0d02649144b0ebc5e33487a572d1a946432dda17","tid":2325120,"uid":53959,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:03:52.000Z","msg":"沒有，沒有，通過！"},{"pid":"e321e2e85f731f8f6472490ae07402690c15985f","tid":2325120,"uid":59887,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:04:20.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦<br />\n仲邊有人會信立法會係有用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ab79b88ddc8ab4c117b15585f9534d82ab9bd3","tid":2325120,"uid":115579,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"到底柒婆同保皇黨極速拎哂d錢，係贏左定攬炒，外國又係咪真係成班官連議員制裁哂佢"},{"pid":"734520a13d2316e63e5960c835fd416062f82602","tid":2325120,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"冇哂攪妙派公屋仲要排咁耐<br />\n對建制派好失望！😡😡"},{"pid":"76c103a88c7f968dec89f6595060086697cbdfaf","tid":2325120,"uid":282637,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:07:24.000Z","msg":"有冇泛民都攞到$啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e772b710d8a2508cc6dac3453be5b95af2ef2e1b","tid":2325120,"uid":34779,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:08:16.000Z","msg":"whatever啦屌"},{"pid":"c82f75dbc78ffe394864e2c7a4575b0b1ed78b1e","tid":2325120,"uid":67816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"誇誇群<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9000bcc8c47ccca312fa5dc854ccc0700190e282","tid":2325120,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b8ab79b88ddc8ab4c117b15585f9534d82ab9bd3","tid":2325120,"uid":115579,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"到底柒婆同保皇黨極速拎哂d錢，係贏左定攬炒，外國又係咪真係成班官連議員制裁哂佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:0